                    <a href="~/images/mo-admin/home.png" class="pointer">
                        <img src="~/images/mo-admin/home.png" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="left-align">I have added the ability to mine the coin via helping me train models - UI subject to change.</p>
                    <a href="~/images/mo-admin/mining.png" class="pointer">
                        <img src="~/images/mo-admin/mining.png" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="left-align">I have added an online wallet but the user can also download the desktop version if he/she doesnt want to hold any details online.</p>
                    <a href="~/images/mo-admin/wallet.png" class="pointer">
                        <img src="~/images/mo-admin/wallet.png" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                    </a>
                </li>
